txt.en: You have made substantial gains, but there is yet much work to be done, if the Zhélruka hope to settle in the formidable Grey Mountains.

Lend a hand in Skarháld by assisting Stráhek the Stout and by completing Wanted Pebbles quests.\n\n<rgb=#FF00FF>This quest will be removed on the weekly reset time, and so must be completed weekly by that time.</rgb>
